_sText:
Hello everybody! This is the latest version of the map.
Fixed bugs with textures. Fixed bugs with sphere.

The map has 4 items:
Item 1: Accelerating pistols.
Item 2: Fire pistols (E). Works as a flamethrower.
Item 3: Repulsive staff (E).
Item 4: Sphere of death(zombie). Slows in a small radius. When touched, it kills.

There is a door with a combination lock.

NEW---
Fixed a server crash. Fixed lags. Fixed staff. Added new secret.

Removed Music.
